<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><author>Lienkhawpau</author>
<hymn_number>263</hymn_number>
<lyrics>[V1]
 1. Khawvel buoiumna khel lam akhun,
 Lalpa'n gam khat A guot a,
 Zie chu A mi telte chenna dingin,
 Zie chu A mi telte chenna dingin,
 Lal lemguot hawih leh thuk chu ahi. (2)

[V2]
 I khawsaknau chu van ahi ngala,
 Zie apat chun Hukdampa I ngak zing,
 Bangkim A thu'n a hih theih ziekin,
 I tawmlai taksau hunsiem lopi in a.

[V3]
 2. Lei avang ling-le-khau a tama,
 Gu leh thang in a dim zo,
 Ginna tha zap in leng sang sang chiet hitiu,
 Ginna tha zap in leng sang sang chiet hitiu,
 Lalpa siem van sang nunnuom akhun. (2)

[V4]
 3. Leng leng leu hing chung thangvan akhun,
 Sietlei hi nungtieng sawn in,
 Thih-le-nat mei zinna khel lam akhun,
 Thih-le-nat mei zinna khel lam akhun,
 Van Lal lung chu su awi ngei hitiu. (2)

[V5]
 4. Chunglam akhun na mit len zingin,
 Hukdampa na ngak hitiu,
 Chunglam, chunglam, chunglam, en zing hitiu,
 Chunglam, chunglam, chunglam, en zing hitiu,
 Ei pui ding van a khawsa I hiu. (2)</lyrics>
<title>I Khawsaknau Van ahi</title>
</song>